Unibail Is Ready to Make Acquisitions, Poitrinal Tells Figaro

-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 
2011-09-20T04:47:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/unibail-is-ready-to-make-acquisitions-poitrinal-tells-figaro.html
Unibail-Rodamco SE (UL)  is ready to make
acquisitions, Chief Executive Officer Guillaume Poitrinal told
French daily Le Figaro in an interview.  Some companies will be forced by the financial crisis to
sell real estate, particularly in  Spain , the newspaper cited
Poitrinal as saying. Unibail is also receiving dossiers on
companies for sale within the industry, Poitrinal told Le
Figaro, without elaborating.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  